    "san": {
      "author": "Dr.S.Sankaranarayan",
      "et":
          "13.8. Absence of  pride; absence of hypocricy; harm-lessness; patience; uprightness; service to the preceptor; purity  [of mind and body]; steadfastness; self-control;"
